      "# Write-Ahead Log Recovery",
      "",
      "Write-ahead logging, or 写前日志, records intent before database pages change so crashes preserve consistency.",
      "",
      "## Proof Obligation",
      "",
      "崩溃一致性证明依赖日志记录先于对应数据页稳定写入。",
      "",
      "```text",
      "flush(log_lsn) before flush(page_lsn)",
      "```",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "WAL and prewrite log are operational names for the same ordering discipline. 预写式日志是中文别名。",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "A corrupt log checksum must stop recovery instead of applying uncertain bytes."
    ],
